Files follow {Entity}Repository.ts pattern. Each entity has a repository implementing I{Entity}Repository interface.

Examples:
- src/repositories/UserRepository.ts: User data access
- src/repositories/OrderRepository.ts: Order data access
- src/repositories/ProductRepository.ts: Product catalogue access
- queries/reports/*.sql: Complex reporting queries (raw SQL)

